    <li>Charitable expenditure for year ending March 2024: approximately £12.3 million.</li>
    <li>Lighthouse service funding:
        <ul>
        <li>From &quot;light dues&quot; levied on commercial vessels calling at British Isles ports</li>
        <li>Based on net registered tonnage</li>
